{
  "texts": [
    "We will compute a smoothing weight matrix W (k) for each k-step according to Eq.",
    "( 18), then we use a list {r 1, r 2, r 3, • • •, r U }.",
    "For each r-value in the list, we derive a new feature node embedding representation of the network structure from Eq.",
    "( 19), denoted as X(u) ∈ R (N l +N d)×(N l +N d).",
    "The feature embeddings obtained from all the r-value are fused to obtain the final feature embedding ẐG ∈ R (N l +N d)×(N l +N d)."
  ]
}